tips.text: Be prepared to wait, always understaffed & the food portions were scripted from Oliver Twist, I literally counted the peas on my plate, last 2 visits have been the same...still better than Harvester..
Get the Sausage and Onion sandwich, then waste some money on the quiz machine.
If you want grilled food try the rock - food arrives part cooked on a superheated ceramic platter, on which you can allow it to cook to your liking.
